### Footnotes

<span id="fn_2489"></span>[381:2490](0070422.htm#fr_2489.md) <span
id="viii.iii.xiv-p0.2"></span>

<span id="viii.iii.xiv-p1"></span> Verses 1 and 3 are given
substantially in <span id="viii.iii.xiv-p1.1"></span>Apostolic
Constitutions, vii. 30. This chapter would seem to belong more properly
before chap. viii.; but the same order of topics is followed in <span
id="viii.iii.xiv-p1.2"></span>Apostolic Constitutions,—a remarkable
proof of literary connection.  

